<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Onboarding — Pragma Studio</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Instrument+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

:root {
  --black:  #111110;
  --white:  #FFFFFF;
  --g1:     #F5F3F0;
  --g2:     #E8E5E0;
  --g3:     #9A9590;
  --g4:     #6B6762;
  --accent: #1847F0;
  --rule:   #E2DED9;
  --green:  #22c55e;
}

html { font-size: 16px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }

body {
  font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
  background: var(--white);
  color: var(--black);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

/* ── TOPBAR ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
.topbar {
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  padding: 22px 64px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.topbar-brand { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.04em; }
.topbar-meta  { font-size: 12px; color: var(--g3); }

/* ── HERO ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
.hero {
  padding: 72px 64px 60px;
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
}

.hero-eyebrow {
  font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px;
}

.hero-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: clamp(42px, 5vw, 68px);
  line-height: 1.06;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  max-width: 600px;
}

.hero-title em { font-style: italic; color: var(--g3); }

.hero-body {
  font-size: 15px; color: var(--g4);
  line-height: 1.75; font-weight: 300;
  max-width: 540px;
}

/* ── QUIZ CONTAINER ────────────────────────────────── */
.quiz-wrap {
  padding: 60px 64px;
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
}

.quiz-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
  gap: 80px;
  align-items: start;
}

.quiz-sidebar {
  position: sticky;
  top: 40px;
}

.quiz-progress {
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.progress-label {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.progress-bar-container {
  height: 8px;
  background: var(--g1);
  border-radius: 4px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.progress-bar {
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--accent);
  transition: width 0.4s ease;
}

.progress-text {
  font-size: 13px; color: var(--g4); font-weight: 500;
}

.quiz-section-badge {
  display: inline-block;
  background: var(--g1);
  color: var(--accent);
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 6px 10px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  margin-top: 32px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.quiz-navigator {
  margin-top: 28px;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
  padding: 16px;
  background: var(--g1);
  border-radius: 8px;
}

.navigator-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.navigator-label {
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--g3);
  margin: 0;
}

.navigator-toggle {
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  color: var(--g4);
  width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  border-radius: 4px;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: bold;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 0;
}

.navigator-toggle:hover {
  border-color: var(--accent);
  color: var(--accent);
}

.navigator-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  gap: 6px;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  max-height: 500px;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.navigator-grid.collapsed {
  max-height: 0;
  opacity: 0;
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.navigator-item {
  aspect-ratio: 1;
  border: 2px solid var(--rule);
  border-radius: 4px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-size: 10px;
  font-weight: 700;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  background: var(--white);
  color: var(--g4);
  min-width: 36px;
  min-height: 36px;
}

.navigator-item:hover:not(.current) {
  border-color: var(--accent);
  transform: scale(1.08);
}

.navigator-item.answered {
  background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.15);
  border-color: var(--green);
  color: #16a34a;
}

.navigator-item.current {
  border-color: var(--accent);
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--white);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.navigator-item.current.answered {
  background: var(--accent);
}

.quiz-estimated {
  margin-top: 20px;
  padding: 16px;
  background: var(--white);
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  border-radius: 8px;
}

.estimated-icon {
  font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--g3); margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.estimated-time {
  font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--black);
}

.estimated-note {
  font-size: 12px; color: var(--g3); margin-top: 4px;
}

/* ── MAIN QUIZ ─────────────────────────────────────── */
.quiz-main {
  display: none;
}

.quiz-main.active {
  display: block;
}

.question-card {
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.question-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 32px;
  line-height: 1.2;
  letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  color: var(--black);
}

.options-hint {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--g3);
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  font-style: italic;
}

.options-group {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.option-label {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 16px;
  padding: 18px 20px;
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  border-radius: 8px;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s ease;
  background: var(--white);
}

.option-label:hover {
  border-color: var(--accent);
  background: var(--g1);
}

.option-label input[type="checkbox"],
.option-label input[type="radio"] {
  margin-top: 2px;
  cursor: pointer;
  accent-color: var(--accent);
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.option-label input:checked + .option-text {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--accent);
}

.option-text {
  font-size: 15px;
  color: var(--black);
  line-height: 1.5;
  flex: 1;
}

.text-input-group {
  display: none;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
}

.text-input-group.active {
  display: block;
}

.text-input-group textarea {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 18px 20px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  border-radius: 8px;
  resize: vertical;
  min-height: 120px;
  color: var(--black);
  transition: border-color 0.2s;
}

.text-input-group textarea:focus {
  outline: none;
  border-color: var(--accent);
  background: var(--g1);
}

.text-input-group textarea::placeholder {
  color: var(--g3);
}

/* ── REVIEW SCREEN ─────────────────────────────────── */
.quiz-review {
  display: none;
}

.quiz-review.active {
  display: block;
}

.review-title {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 48px;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  margin-bottom: 40px;
  color: var(--black);
}

.review-section {
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.review-section-title {
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--accent);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
  padding-bottom: 12px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
}

.review-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 24px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.review-card {
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 24px;
  background: var(--white);
}

.review-card-label {
  font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.review-card-question {
  font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.review-card-answer {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--g4);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.review-actions {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.btn-copy {
  padding: 18px 24px;
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--white);
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 10px;
}

.btn-copy:hover {
  background: #0935c9;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.btn-download {
  padding: 18px 24px;
  background: var(--white);
  color: var(--accent);
  border: 1px solid var(--accent);
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 10px;
}

.btn-download:hover {
  background: var(--g1);
}

.completion-box {
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 32px 24px;
  text-align: center;
  background: var(--g1);
}

.completion-icon {
  font-size: 32px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.completion-text {
  font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--black);
}

.completion-subtext {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--g4);
  margin-top: 8px;
}

/* ── BUTTONS ────────────────────────────────────────── */
.quiz-controls {
  display: flex;
  gap: 12px;
  margin-top: 48px;
}

.btn-nav {
  padding: 14px 28px;
  border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  background: var(--white);
  color: var(--black);
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;
  display: none;
}

.btn-nav.visible {
  display: inline-block;
}

.btn-nav:hover {
  border-color: var(--accent);
  color: var(--accent);
}

.btn-next {
  flex: 1;
  padding: 14px 28px;
  background: var(--accent);
  color: var(--white);
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-family: 'Instrument Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 600;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.2s;
}

.btn-next:hover {
  background: #0935c9;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

/* ── FOOTER ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
.doc-footer {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 40px;
  align-items: center;
  max-width: 1280px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 48px 64px;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--g4);
}

.foot-brand { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--black); margin-bottom: 4px; }
.foot-tagline { font-size: 12px; color: var(--g3); }

.foot-contact { text-align: right; }
.foot-contact a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
.foot-contact a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

/* ── RESPONSIVE ────────────────────────────────────── */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .topbar, .hero, .quiz-wrap, .doc-footer {
    padding-left: 48px;
    padding-right: 48px;
  }

  .quiz-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .quiz-sidebar {
    position: static;
  }

  .doc-footer {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .foot-contact {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .navigator-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
  }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .topbar, .hero, .quiz-wrap, .doc-footer {
    padding-left: 32px;
    padding-right: 32px;
  }

  .topbar {
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero {
    padding: 48px 32px 40px;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .hero-body {
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .question-title {
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .review-title {
    font-size: 36px;
  }

  .quiz-wrap {
    padding: 40px 32px;
  }

  .quiz-grid {
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .quiz-sidebar {
    order: 2;
  }

  .quiz-main {
    order: 1;
  }

  .review-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .review-actions {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .quiz-controls {
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .btn-nav {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 120px;
  }

  .btn-next {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .navigator-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(8, 1fr);
    gap: 5px;
  }

  .navigator-item {
    min-width: 32px;
    min-height: 32px;
    font-size: 9px;
  }

  .quiz-navigator {
    margin-top: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding: 12px;
  }

  .quiz-estimated {
    margin-top: 16px;
    padding: 12px;
  }

  .estimated-time {
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .estimated-note {
    font-size: 11px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .topbar, .hero, .quiz-wrap, .doc-footer {
    padding-left: 20px;
    padding-right: 20px;
  }

  .topbar {
    padding: 16px 20px;
  }

  .topbar-brand {
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .topbar-meta {
    font-size: 10px;
  }

  .hero {
    padding: 40px 20px 32px;
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 10px;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .hero-body {
    font-size: 13px;
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .quiz-wrap {
    padding: 32px 20px;
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .quiz-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .quiz-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: var(--white);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .quiz-progress {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .progress-label {
    font-size: 10px;
  }

  .progress-text {
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .quiz-section-badge {
    margin-top: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 8px;
    padding: 4px 8px;
  }

  .quiz-navigator {
    margin-top: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    padding: 10px;
    background: var(--g1);
  }

  .navigator-header {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .navigator-label {
    font-size: 9px;
  }

  .navigator-toggle {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .navigator-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(8, 1fr);
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .navigator-grid.collapsed {
    max-height: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .navigator-item {
    min-width: 28px;
    min-height: 28px;
    font-size: 8px;
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .quiz-estimated {
    margin-top: 12px;
    padding: 10px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }

  .estimated-icon {
    font-size: 9px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .estimated-time {
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .estimated-note {
    font-size: 10px;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .question-card {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .question-title {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .options-hint {
    font-size: 11px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .options-group {
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .option-label {
    padding: 14px 16px;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .option-label input[type="checkbox"],
  .option-label input[type="radio"] {
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
  }

  .option-text {
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .text-input-group textarea {
    padding: 14px 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    min-height: 100px;
  }

  .quiz-controls {
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .btn-nav {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .btn-next {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .review-title {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .review-section-title {
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .review-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .review-card {
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
  }

  .review-card-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .review-card-question {
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .review-card-answer {
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .review-actions {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .btn-copy,
  .btn-download {
    padding: 14px 16px;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .completion-box {
    padding: 20px 16px;
  }

  .completion-icon {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .completion-text {
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .completion-subtext {
    font-size: 12px;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .doc-footer {
    padding: 32px 20px;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .foot-brand {
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .foot-tagline {
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  .foot-contact {
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .topbar, .hero, .quiz-wrap, .doc-footer {
    padding-left: 16px;
    padding-right: 16px;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 24px;
  }

  .hero-body {
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .quiz-sidebar {
    top: -20px;
    padding: 0 -16px;
    margin: 0 -16px 16px;
  }

  .navigator-grid {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);
  }

  .question-title {
    font-size: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .option-label {
    padding: 12px 14px;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .review-title {
    font-size: 24px;
  }

  .quiz-wrap {
    padding: 24px 16px;
  }

  .quiz-grid {
    gap: 20px;
  }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- TOPBAR -->
<div class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-brand">Pragma Studio</div>
  <div class="topbar-meta">Onboarding del proyecto</div>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">Cuestionario de descubrimiento</div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">Confirmemos los detalles <em>antes de arrancar</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-body">Necesitamos validar todas las respuestas para asegurar que el sistema sea exactamente como lo necesitás. Usa el navegador de preguntas para ir donde quieras. Una vez completado, tendrás un resumen para compartir con el equipo.</p>
</div>

<!-- QUIZ -->
<div class="quiz-wrap">
  <div class="quiz-grid">
    
    <!-- SIDEBAR -->
    <div class="quiz-sidebar">
      <div class="quiz-progress">
        <div class="progress-label">Progreso</div>
